p>',232,10,'To differentiate them from the customers.','2020-12-07 01:47:05','2020-12-07 01:47:05',0,'1607305625305-smp B INDONESIA 1 7.jpg',0),(1650,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>The following text is for Questions 8 to 11.</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Asep Sunandar Sunarya is Indonesia&rsquo;s most famous puppeteer in &ldquo;wayang golek&rdquo;, a traditional Indonesia wooden puppet show originating from the West Java province. He was born in September 1955 in a small kampong near Bandung the capital of West Java. Asep followed in his father&rsquo;s footstep and become a puppeteer while he was a teenager.</p>\n<p>Asep is a gifted storyteller. He moves his puppets through rough fight scenes, where he throws his puppets and spin them in the air.</p>\n<p>Asep like to combine modernity and tradition in performing wayang golek. Sometimes, his puppets have the face of a clown, sticking out their tongues and he even moves puppet heads during his performance. His performances are always entertaining as well as educational.</p>\n<p>Asep has been invited to perform not only throughout Indonesia, but also in European, American, and Asian countries. As a master puppeteer, he usually performs alone, but because the length of the performances and the hundreads of puppets that he employs, Asep always has assistants to help him.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The text describes ...</p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'a famous wayang golek puppeteer','2020-12-07 01:51:51','2020-12-07 01:51:51',0,'1607305910805-smp B INDONESIA 1 8.jpg',0),(1651,'<p>How are Asep Sunandar&rsquo;s wayang golek performances?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'Entertaining and educating people.','2020-12-07 01:54:57','2020-12-07 01:54:57',0,'1607306097713-smp B INDONESIA 1 9.jpg',0),(1652,'<p>The main idea of paragraph 3 is ...</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'Asep mixes the tradition modernity','2020-12-07 01:58:55','2020-12-07 01:58:55',0,'1607306334758-smp B INDONESIA 1 10.jpg',0)