. Most of the casualties were children and elderly people.</p>\n<p>For thousand of people in Bhopal, that night was like any other night. But a little after midnight, the poisonous gas slowly leaked into the atmosphere. Hundreds of people woke up from their sleep coughing and vomiting. Others woke up with eyes watering and some temporarily blinded. Many people tried to escape the poisonous clouds by getting out of town. They tried to get any kind of vehicle to get out of the town to save their lives. Hundreds of poor people tried to flee the town on foot but many of them dropped on the way.</p>\n<p>What is the text about?</p>',232,10,'An explosion at the union carbide factory in Bhopal, India.','2020-12-07 02:48:16','2020-12-07 02:48:16',0,'1607309296204-smp B INDONESIA 1 18.jpg',0),(1661,'<p>&ldquo;Hundreds of poor people tried of <u>flee </u>to the town on foot. ...&rdquo;</p>\n<p>The underlined word means ...</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'run away','2020-12-07 03:54:21','2020-12-07 03:54:21',0,'1607313260983-smp B INDONESIA 1 19.jpg',0),(1662,'<p>Why did the victims of the accident in Bhoppal suffered from lung injury?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'Because the chemical gas from the explosion effected their breathing.','2020-12-07 03:55:45','2020-12-07 03:55:45',0,'1607313345387-smp B INDONESIA 1 20.jpg',0),(1663,'<p>What is the main idea of paragraph three?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'The victims of the accident tried hard to save their lives.','2020-12-07 05:51:38','2020-12-07 05:51:38',0,'1607320298777-smp B INDONESIA 1 21.jpg',0),(1664,'<p>Based on the text, we can conclude that poor people dropped on the way to the town because</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'they went to town on foot','2020-12-07 05:54:42','2020-12-07 05:54:42',0,'1607320482215-smp B INDONESIA 1 22.jpg',0),(1665,'<h1>The following text is for Questions 23 and 24.</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"http://103.41.207.247:3000/1607320932819-smp B INDONESIA 1 23.jpg\" alt=\"1607320932819-smp B INDONESIA 1 23.jpg