help them. Kiai Gede heard about the couple&rsquo;s bad behavior.</p>\n<p>Soon he visited the couple. He met them when the couple was working in the field. Kiai Gede talked to the couple. He reminded the couple not to be arrogant, but the couple ignored him. They said nothing to Kiai Gede. Kiai Gede got very angry. Then he said, &ldquo;You two are like temples. You do not listen to me&rdquo;. Right after he said those words, an incredible thing happened. Slowly, Jaka and Dewi turned into temples. Because the temples stood among the pari, people then named them as Pari Temples.</p>\n<p>What did Jaka Pandelengan and his wife do to be rich?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'Planted pari seeds.','2020-12-07 06:23:50','2020-12-07 06:23:50',0,'1607322230262-smp B INDONESIA 1 25.jpg',0),(1668,'<p>The couple becomes temples because ...</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'Kiai Gede liked them','2020-12-07 06:26:12','2020-12-07 06:26:12',0,'1607322372278-smp B INDONESIA 1 26.jpg',0),(1669,'<p>&ldquo; ... , an incredible thing happened.&rdquo; The underlined word means ...</p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'unbelievable','2020-12-07 06:30:03','2020-12-07 06:30:03',0,'1607322603738-smp B INDONESIA 1 27.jpg',0),(1670,'<p>What can we learn from the story?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'We have to listen to our parent’s advice.','2020-12-07 06:34:47','2020-12-07 06:34:47',0,'1607322886528-smp B INDONESIA 1 28.jpg',0),(1671,'<h1>The following text is for Questions 29 to 31.</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A young and succesful man was driving in his new car when he saw some children playing between parked cars. Suddenly a stone hit the car&rsquo;s side door. He stopped and got out of the car. Angrily he pulled one of the nearest boy and shouted, &ldquo;Look! What you have done to my car! Why did you do it?&rdquo; The young boy apologized. &ldquo;Please mister ... please I need your help&rdquo;. The little boy cried. He is so sick and I couldn&rsquo;t 