ttle water to grow.</p>\n<p>Aloe vera is a short-stemmed succelent plant growing to 60-100 cm tall. Spreading by offsets, the stems are thick and fleshy, green to grey-green, with some varieties showing white flecks on the upper and lower stem surfaces. Aloe vera is a multifunctional plant. It can be used to cure a wound caused by burning. Using aloe vera to heal the wound is easy and simple. Pick the leaves, peel the made into healthy drink to prevent rheumatism and diabetes because it countains vitamin and minerals. Generally, the drink helps to repair the damaged cells and makes the organs of the human body work well.</p>\n<p>Aloe vera can also make our hair thick too. Apply it over the scalp and massage it gently so it could soak thoroughly. Ten minutes later, rinse the hair.</p>\n<p>What does the text mostly tell us about?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'Aloe Vera.','2020-12-07 07:20:53','2020-12-07 07:20:53',0,'1607325653538-smp B INDONESIA 1 34.jpg',0),(1677,'<p>Where does aloe vera grow?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'In dry areas and warm climates.','2020-12-07 07:22:23','2020-12-07 07:22:23',0,'1607325742955-smp B INDONESIA 1 35.jpg',0),(1678,'<p>&ldquo;It can be used for curing the wounds caused by burning.&rdquo; From the underlined word, we can conclude that ...</p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'aloe vera is a medical herb','2020-12-07 07:23:50','2020-12-07 07:23:50',0,'1607325830662-smp B INDONESIA 1 36.jpg',0),(1679,'<p>What does paragraph three tell us about?</p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',232,10,'The advantages of aloe vera.','2020-12-07 07:27:12','2020-12-07 07:27:12',0,'1607326001297-smp B INDONESIA 1 37.jpg',0),(1680,'<p><strong>The following text is for Questions 38 to 41. </strong></p>\n<p>The Earth receives heat from the sun and reflects some of this heat into space. Carbon dioxide and other gases in the air act as a blanket to hold onto some 